config CHARGING_CONTROL
	tristate "Infinity Charging Control Driver"
	depends on POWER_SUPPLY && SYSFS
	default m
	help
	  Infinity Kernel charging control for SM8250-AC (Snapdragon 860).
	  Provides 4 charging modes: Normal, Balance, Performance, Game.
	  Also supports charging bypass (discharge while plugged in).
	  
	  Modes:
	  - Normal: Default charging behavior
	  - Balance: Reduced charge current, extended battery life
	  - Performance: Full speed charging with thermal limits
	  - Game: Bypass charging - runs on wall power without charging battery
	  
	  Control via /sys/class/power_supply/battery/charging_mode
	  or via IOCTL through /dev/infinity_charging.